title: Private Chefs of Beverly Hills
overview: Private Chefs of Beverly Hills will follow Big City Chefs, Beverly Hills' premiere private chef placement agency. On-call at all hours of the day, this group of talented chefs cater to the over-the-top and eclectic clientele in Los Angeles' most posh neighborhood. Viewers will get a glimpse into the secret and high-demand world of culinary glamour where anything is possible.
